quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  54,41,Kanti nakubantu bakwaFir’awn kwafika isilumkiso
  54,42,"Bayala imiqondiso yeThu yonke, Sabahlasela ke ngohlaselo lwaloWo Unobunganga, Unamandla"
  54,43,"Ingaba (abantu) abangakholwayo benu bangcono kunabayaa bamandulo, okanye ninogonyo oluvela kwiziBhalo"
  54,44,"Okanye bathi: “Thina silibandla elixhasanayo,” kusini na"
  54,45,"(Elo) bandlana labo liza koyiswa, kwaye baza kuza ngemiva (babaleke)"
  54,46,"Kodwa iYure lixesha labo elimisiweyo, kwaye iYure leyo ingaphaya ngokonakalisa yaye ikrakra ngakumbi"
  54,47,Inene izaphula-mthetho zisekulahlekeni nasempambanweni
  54,48,"NgeMini abaya kurhuqelwa eMlilweni ngobuso babo kuya (kuthiwa kubo): “Ngcamlani ukuchukunyiswa sisiHogo kaloku”"
  54,49,Inene Sidale zonke izinto ngommiselo (wento eziya kuba yiyo)
  54,50,"Ukanti\tumyalelo\tweThu\tuba\tmnye\tjwi\tube\tngathi kukuqhwanyaza kweliso"
  54,51,"Kananjalo Sele Sabatshabalalisa abanjengani, ukhona phofu za kukhumbula"
  54,52,Kananjalo yonke into abayenzayo ibhaliwe emacwecweni
  54,53,Kwaye nto nganye encinane (nenkulu) ibhaliwe
  54,54,Inene amalungisa aya kuba phakathi kwemiyezo nemilambo
  54,55,"Esihlalweni sentlonipheko ecaleni kukaSobunganga, uSomandla"